---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Accessibility Statement - SuperInstance.AI">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h1 class="heading-1 mb-8">Accessibility Statement</h1>

      <p class="text-body mb-6">
        SuperInstance.AI is committed to making advanced AI and mathematics education accessible to everyone.
        This statement outlines our accessibility features and ongoing efforts to ensure full inclusion.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="card-hover">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our platform follows Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA standards, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>✅ Text alternatives for non-text content</li>
            <li>✅ Captions for videos</li>
            <li>✅ Minimum color contrast ratios (4.5:1)</li>
            <li>✅ Keyboard accessibility for all features</li>
            <li>✅ Clear page titles and headings</li>
            <li>✅ Consistent navigation</li>
            <li>✅ Error identification and correction</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card-hover">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">Assistive Technology Support</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our platform works seamlessly with:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>✅ Screen readers (JAWS, NVDA, VoiceOver)</li>
            <li>✅ Screen magnifiers</li>
            <li>✅ Voice recognition software</li>
            <li>✅ Eye tracking devices</li>
            <li>✅ Switch navigation</li>
            <li>✅ Keyboard-only navigation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card-hover">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">Keyboard Navigation</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Navigate our site using keyboard:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li><strong>Tab:</strong> Navigate between links and form controls</li>
            <li><strong>Enter/Space:</strong> Activate buttons and links</li>
            <li><strong>Arrow Keys:</strong> Navigate dropdown menus</li>
            <li><strong>Esc:</strong> Close modal dialogs</li>
            <li><strong>Alt + R:</strong> Toggle reading mode</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card-hover">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">Adaptive Features</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Platform automatically adapts based on user needs:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>✅ Low bandwidth optimizations</li>
            <li>✅ Offline mode for critical content</li>
            <li>✅ Text-to-speech integration</li>
            <li>✅ Reading mode for reduced distraction</li>
            <li>✅ High contrast and dark modes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card-hover md:col-span-2">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">Text-to-Speech Integration</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Click the <strong><span aria-hidden="true">🔊</span> listen</strong> button in the bottom right corner
            to have any page read aloud. This feature helps:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>Students with reading difficulties</li>
            <li>Multimodal learning preferences</li>
            <li>Non-native English speakers</li>
            <li>Eye-free learning environments</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card-hover md:col-span-2 mt-8">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">Ongoing Improvements</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We're continuously improving accessibility. Current initiatives:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600"
            <li>🔄 Regular accessibility audits with industry tools</li>
            <li>👥 User testing with people with disabilities</li>
            <li>🎯 Multi-language screen reader support</li>
            <li>🔭 Accessibility score targets: 95+ Lighthouse score</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Provide Feedback</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Help us improve! Report accessibility issues:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a
              href="mailto:accessibility@superinstance.ai"
              class="btn btn-primary"
              aria-label="Email accessibility feedback to SuperInstance.AI team"
            >
              Email: accessibility@superinstance.ai
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="btn btn-outline"
              aria-label="Use contact form for accessibility feedback"
            >
              Contact Form
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }
</style><style>
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background-color: #2563eb;
    color: white;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #1d4ed8;
  }
  .btn-outline {
    border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    color: #374151;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    background-color: #f3f4f6;
  }
